### DELETE DOCUMENT (OWNER/EDITOR ONLY)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/documents/docId
Authorization: Bearer token

### GET ALL TASKS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer token

### GET PROJECT TASKS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/project/projectId
Authorization: Bearer token

### GET DOCUMENT TASKS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/document/docId
Authorization: Bearer token

### UPDATE TASK
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/taskId
Authorization: Bearer token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task",
  "status": "done"
}

### DELETE TASK
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/taskId
Authorization: Bearer token